001package org.consensusj.bitcoin.json.pojo;
002
003import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonCreator;
004import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonIgnoreProperties;
005import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty;
006
007/**
008 * POJO for `getnetworkinfo` RPC response.
009 * Warning: `network` and `address` will be upgraded to POJOs in the future
010 */
011public class NetworkInfo {
012    private final int version;
013    private final String subVersion;
014    private final int protocolVersion;
015    private final int timeOffset;
016    private final int connections;
017    private final String proxy;
018    private final int relayFee;
019    private final byte[] localServices;
020    private final Object[]  network;
021    private final Object[]  address;
022
023    @JsonCreator
024    public NetworkInfo(@JsonProperty("version")         int version,
025                       @JsonProperty("subversion")      String subVersion,
026                       @JsonProperty("protocolversion") int protocolVersion,
027                       @JsonProperty("timeOffset")      int timeOffset,
028                       @JsonProperty("connections")     int connections,
029                       @JsonProperty("proxy")           String proxy,
030                       @JsonProperty("relayFee")        int relayFee,
031                       @JsonProperty("localServices")   byte[] localServices,
032                       @JsonProperty("network")         Object[] network,
033                       @JsonProperty("address")         Object[] address) {
034        this.version = version;
035        this.subVersion = subVersion;
036        this.protocolVersion = protocolVersion;
037        this.timeOffset = timeOffset;
038        this.connections = connections;
039        this.proxy = proxy;
040        this.relayFee = relayFee;
041        this.localServices = localServices;
042        this.network = network;
043        this.address = address;
044    }
045
046    public int getVersion() {
047        return version;
048    }
049
050    public String getSubVersion() {
051        return subVersion;
052    }
053
054    public int getProtocolVersion() {
055        return protocolVersion;
056    }
057
058    public int getTimeOffset() {
059        return timeOffset;
060    }
061
062    public int getConnections() {
063        return connections;
064    }
065
066    public String getProxy() {
067        return proxy;
068    }
069
070    public int getRelayFee() {
071        return relayFee;
072    }
073
074    public byte[] getLocalServices() {
075        return localServices;
076    }
077
078    public Object[] getNetwork() {
079        return network;
080    }
081
082    public Object[] getAddress() {
083        return address;
084    }
085}
